{"id":250401,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/奇闻录-盛世一景-9-5/","date":"2012-09-06T04:17:55Z","modified":"2012-09-06T04:17:55Z","title":"奇闻录 | 盛世一景 9-5","content":"<p><p>2012年3月3日，手持钢枪、身穿军装的“中国首善”陈光标亮相湖南卫视《锋尚之王》节目录制现场。他自称是雷锋的粉丝，从事慈善事业也是受到雷锋精神的感召。<span></span></p>\n<p>这位极富争议的企业家系江苏黄埔再生资源利用公司董事长，自称陈低碳。育有两子：陈环保、陈环境。陈光标说希望借此名字告诉世人保护环境的重要。</p>\n<p><img title=\"\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/ca.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"550\" /></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=01WATDv-smI:TIzLuABaz9Y:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" na